rce attacks to determine future session IDs."]}],"security_levels":["SL-C (SI, control system) 1: Not Selected","SL-C (SI, control system) 2: SR 3.8","SL-C (SI, control system) 3: SR 3.8 (1) (2)","SL-C (SI, control system) 4: SR 3.8 (1) (2) (3)"]} 
